{"tid":1441514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 愉景新城稱埋伏嘅黑警只係「去厠所」","createTime":"2019-08-10T16:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T00:56:03.000Z","uid":79369,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cbe9043b1965cca2767d63649e773e71046ace90","tid":1441514,"uid":79369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:24:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有哂圖班黑警伏喺度，你同我講佢哋係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">去厠所</span></strong></span>?!<br />\n屌你老母愉景新城!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XEpd0aS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXEpd0aS.jpg&h=dd4bc47f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚10點04分，有數名警察從美環街入口進入商場，他們在使用最就近的洗手間五分鐘後，全部迅速離開。商場保安人員得悉他們進場後，已即時上前交涉，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警察表示有急切生理需要</span></span>，他們使用洗手間後已即時離開商場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mufTZ9K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmufTZ9K.jpg&h=9e195dc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"febc5673e9fba08043b04571c80433954badd01c","tid":1441514,"uid":79369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:26:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c5ecabf66aeb284d668f3c1419a1aace8f9a3e2","tid":1441514,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:28:26.000Z","msg":"得張圖佢話佢等埋其他狗都得<br />\n有片會可信啲"},{"pid":"1237d6eb10268494ff2374b6675c8c900bc3d70b","tid":1441514,"uid":52276,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"嘩，係商場入面容乜易見人就打，放tear gas 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以後都唔敢去&hellip;"},{"pid":"45c5d184430e26691566321c9e5d145d9f321e43","tid":1441514,"uid":79369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:32:03.000Z","msg":"仲話即時離開? 企撚哂起度喎<br />\n同埋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">愉景新城對面就係警局，點解唔返入警局廁所</span></span>??"},{"pid":"74a17b0ff79dad09a53de388c0bf0487e136e62d","tid":1441514,"uid":149806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"愉城一出對面就係警局，點解唔去警局廁所？<br />\n<br />\n況且愉城係親子商場，好多家長小朋友去食飯去玩，咁樣實嚇親佢地！根本愉城就係為警察講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ef334e87e3a31ce8e6f6181be5cc331bf04cab","tid":1441514,"uid":79369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1237d6eb10268494ff2374b6675c8c900bc3d70b","tid":1441514,"uid":52276,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"嘩，係商場入面容乜易見人就打，放tear gas 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以後都唔敢去&hellip;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:36:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">隨時仲要比人拖入暗角打獲</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd3b6927d4b26487daf1beac7d815338f893b43","tid":1441514,"uid":79369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:43:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bcdda47a06d9521d6afc2e9257f0bdfb993cb001","tid":1441514,"uid":79369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:43:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8edf5f62394af007b3899e6750787bcda57c89dc","tid":1441514,"uid":79369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93ba971e3ca0509f26cdd3c6a0a36e781c81eed","tid":1441514,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T00:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}